Package: sshm
Version: ${VERSION}
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: ${ARCH}
Maintainer: Sn0wAlice <github@sn0w.io>
Homepage: https://github.com/Sn0wAlice/sshm
Description: Fast SSH + Docker + Incus + Kubernetes manager for the terminal
 SSHM is a terminal UI application to manage and connect to SSH hosts,
 Docker containers (local and remote over SSH), Incus instances, and
 Kubernetes / k3s pods — all from one keyboard-driven interface.
 Features include fuzzy search, deeply nested folders, persistent
 tunnels, multi-hop ProxyJump, ssh-agent integration, hardware-key
 detection, host reachability with SSH banner probing, theme
 customization, English/French i18n, and export to ~/.ssh/config.
